  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    UK nationals in the EEA and Switzerland: access to higher education and 19+ further education
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Access to higher education and 19+ further education, for UK nationals coming to England from the EU, Iceland, Liechtenstein, Norway (EEA) or Switzerland. Includes changes from the start of the 2021 to 2022 academic year.</p>

  </div>
</div>

